  "title": "Accounts Executive (Japanese speaking) |Upto $5,000",
  "description": "<p>【Job ID: 1418579】</p><p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Prepare and process accounts payable and receivable transactions, ensuring accuracy of financial data.</li><li>Reconcile accounts and maintain accurate financial records.</li><li>Manage daily accounting operations, including weekly payment submissions and data entry.</li><li>Assist with budgeting, cash flow forecasting, and fixed asset planning.</li><li>Liaise with external agents such as accounting firms, tax agents, and auditors.</li><li>Support month-end and year-end closing activities and assist in preparing financial reports.</li><li>Handle quarterly GST submissions and corporate tax matters.</li><li>Collaborate with external auditors for timely year-end closing and reporting.</li><li>Coordinate with finance teams at headquarters in Japan and overseas subsidiaries.</li><li>Ensure compliance with accounting policies and regulations.</li><li>Provide general administrative support to the accounting department.</li><li>Assist with ad hoc reporting and other duties as assigned by management.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 2–4 years of experience in accounting or related roles.</li><li>Proficiency in Japanese for liaising with Japanese-speaking stakeholders at headquarters.</li><li>Advanced skills in Microsoft Office (Excel, Word, PowerPoint).</li><li>Strong analytical and problem-solving abilities.</li><li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills.</li><li>Ability to manage multiple tasks and prioritise effectively.</li></ul><p>——————————-</p><p>We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified. However, rest assured that all applications will be updated to our resume bank for future opportunities.</p><p>Please kindly refer to the Privacy Policy of Good Job Creations for your reference: https://goodjobcreations.com.sg/en/privacy-policy/</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Ito (Sherpa) Yurika</p><p>EA Personnel Registration Number: R25159178</p><p>EA License No.: 07C5771</p>",
